    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it really shows! It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person than in the photos. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love every mile in it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
