      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster. Mechanically uncompromising and meticulously preserved, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
