    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it waxed and garage-kept its whole life. It drives like an absolute dream and has been totally babied. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and is ready to hit the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 44500.0,
